name: The Void
description: The Void, also known as Purple Apollo 13, is a sativa-dominant hybrid cross between Apollo 13 and Querkle from TGA Genetics. It tastes similar to grape saltwater taffy and provides a soaring, motivational high.
descriptionPlain: The Void, also known as Purple Apollo 13, is a sativa-dominant hybrid cross between Apollo 13 and Querkle from TGA Genetics. It tastes similar to grape saltwater taffy and provides a soaring, motivational high.

highlightedReviews.text:
Without a doubt, a killer. Mine was grown hydroponically, not in dirt, so the experience is different, slightly. Its is a 60/40 hybrid favoring indica. Mixed with Querkle and Apollo 13 (correct me if I'm wrong, thx).

The bud itself, has almost a 'caramel' hue to it, dusted white. (7/10)

 Smells like a skunk fucked a skunk. (8.5/10)

.33 grams The Void in clean Wooden Pipe:
Earthy, slightly sweet undertone, interesting piney overtone, medium smoke, reminds me of a kush. (8.5/10)

:07 - initial effects: pleasant buzz in head, felt in front temple next to eyes, probably great for Glaucoma...
:10 - cotton mouth, elevated heartbeat, (no paranoia, or anxiety) good for High Blood Pressure...
:15 - buzz definitely peaking quick. Very relaxing and elevating, would be a great 'doing something' smoke.
:35 - peak is over, clean even high. The Indy hits you more than the Sativa. Great party smoke, I feel sociable and focused, but WAY stoned.
1:00 - STONED
1:30 - ...
1:45 - PROFIT!!!
2:30 - coming down, I'm glued to the couch watching Discovery, don't remember when I started....
Overall BUZZ.......---- (8/10)

OVERALL CROP------ 8/10

Ok... this is the ‚Äúreal‚Äù review!  What I had before must have been mislabeled.  This is an exceptional hybrid!  Made me very talkative (not able to hide the stoney speak & giggles), happy, pain, anxiety & nausea free!! 

This makes me cough my lungs out in flower, but it is a kinda stale pre-roll. Think it would be great in concentrate! 

Damn! 5 drags & I‚Äôm hitüòÇ.... a creeper that lasts awhile! Lookin for this again. Very happy, social, peaceful.  I wanna go sit in the hammock now.
